{"tid":873962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"哥本哈根膺最佳旅遊城市 深圳居次","createTime":"2018-10-23T23:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T23:39:56.000Z","uid":17641,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4bd5c7229599c3a506661ea8307c190435794f12","tid":873962,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T23:21:00.000Z","msg":"【本報綜合報道】被譽為旅遊界天書的《孤獨星球》（Lonely Planet）近日公布全球十大最佳旅遊城市，其中丹麥首都哥本哈根居首，深圳緊隨其後，而塞爾維亞的諾維薩德（Novi Sad）則奪得第三名<br />\n<br />\n譽為平價版香港夜生活<br />\n文中指出，哥本哈根有一個前身是船塢的美食及手作市場樂福沙樂恩（Refshaleoen），把當地的街頭小食文化發揚光大。當地又有歷史悠久的主題公園蒂沃利花園（Tivoli Gardens），即使是廢物處理中心阿邁厄峰（Amager Bakke）頂層，也建有人工滑雪場及行山區。<br />\n<br />\n至於深圳則被該本旅遊界天書喻為中國版「硅谷」，城內盡是新設計、高科技和創意產業；深圳現已由「香港夜生活平價版」，轉變為嶄新藝術區、型格咖啡店林立的地方。其餘入圍的亞洲城市，尼泊爾首都加德滿都則進佔第五位。"},{"pid":"2633f6de2865373ad0093b61885d911ee225c20a","tid":873962,"uid":182499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T23:23:33.000Z","msg":"Wtf?"},{"pid":"a7ee4ffe9820303cec3c5c1ae477e10fad69883d","tid":873962,"uid":136186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T23:32:47.000Z","msg":"做馬"},{"pid":"3a7a1ce7517191164771249f5fc5a37e4816cae8","tid":873962,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T23:34:27.000Z","msg":"收錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb110aa89dc012c00550db57b4d796eff6a6dca2","tid":873962,"uid":42283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T23:35:18.000Z","msg":"收幾多"},{"pid":"e33a62fcb3c2c285b9fda040ffb9ce26fbbeaecd","tid":873962,"uid":41818,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T23:35:26.000Z","msg":"東京第二我就服"},{"pid":"25dc83f789de92a98846c4a37732aabc6d73f3d6","tid":873962,"uid":25038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T23:37:13.000Z","msg":"真心想知，深圳可以有咩睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"101ea1231efb3aa6e4f6466e540e97872e83a25c","tid":873962,"uid":167032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25dc83f789de92a98846c4a37732aabc6d73f3d6","tid":873962,"uid":25038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T23:37:13.000Z","msg":"真心想知，深圳可以有咩睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T23:37:44.000Z","msg":"三和大神"},{"pid":"5564864cc59d9c41438907a04d2c7351c2ce5968","tid":873962,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T23:39:04.000Z","msg":"因為深圳有喜茶"},{"pid":"7f57f0180d5ceeb394dfa662bc327df71c43bc6c","tid":873962,"uid":53901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T23:39:32.000Z","msg":"淨講交通<br />\n已經唔覺值第二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65375c9880919ff65e3fb667cd459d162a08c24","tid":873962,"uid":155919,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T23:39:56.000Z","msg":"最近的確多左鬼佬去深圳搞startup或者整tech野<br />\n因為近生產線<br />\n有個youtuber係深圳由零砌到部ip之後越黎越多人知"}]}